name: DangerousMechanismOfInjury
title: Dangerous Mechanism of Injury
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent a dangerous mechanism of injury.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may be used as a Quality Data Model (QDM) attribute.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts related to dangerous mechanism of injury, including those indicating ejection from a motor vehicle, a pedestrian struck, and a fall from a height of more than 3 feet or 5 stairs.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
